spx.utils

Interface SourceType


  • public interface SourceType
    Definitions for the source type values used in the sourceType field of a Heartbeat.

    These constants are kept in sync with the SPX_RIB_SOURCE_TYPE_... constants in "SPxRib.h".

    See Also:
    Heartbeat
